  "text": "Membrane preparation and adenosine A 1 receptor binding assay. Approximately 3 ml of packed cells were used to prepare an adipocyte crude plasma membrane fraction, as described by Dong and Carey (8) . The fraction was resuspended to 2 mg protein/ml and stored at Ϫ80°C until being assayed for A 1 receptor binding kinetics [CITATION_1] .",
